          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-white p-6" style="border-color: #e5e5e5;">
            <div class="mx-auto flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl" style="background: #7c3aed12; border: 1px solid #7c3aed2e; color: #7c3aed;"><Icon name="flag" size={24} /></div>
            <div class="mt-3 text-sm font-bold" style="color: #0a0a0a;">National Treasure</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-xs" style="color: #737373;">Top 1 % France Lovable</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-white p-6" style="border-color: #e5e5e5;">
            <div class="mx-auto flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl" style="background: #c026d312; border: 1px solid #c026d32e; color: #c026d3;"><Icon name="mic" size={24} /></div>
            <div class="mt-3 text-sm font-bold" style="color: #0a0a0a;">Record YouTube FROT</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-xs" style="color: #737373;">Webinaire 4,8/5 satisfaction</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-white p-6" style="border-color: #e5e5e5;">
            <div class="mx-auto flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl" style="background: #6d28d912; border: 1px solid #6d28d92e; color: #6d28d9;"><Icon name="graduation" size={24} /></div>
            <div class="mt-3 text-sm font-bold" style="color: #0a0a0a;">23 certifications IA</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-xs" style="color: #737373;">Anthropic · Make · Lovable</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
